            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>Barbados has no systematic declassification of government documents.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Foreign Trade: 1 Culloden Road, St. Michael.</p>
                <p>Archives Department: Black Rock, St. Michael. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should contact the Ministry of Foreign Affairs to request access to
                    documents. For pre-independence documents, researchers should write to the UK
                    National Archives.</p>
            </div>
